Package api

Class DWGraph_DS

java.lang.Object
api.DWGraph_DS
All Implemented Interfaces:
directed_weighted_graph, java.io.Serializable
public class DWGraph_DS
extends java.lang.Object
implements directed_weighted_graph, java.io.Serializable
This class implements a directed weighted graph. Every graph contains a map of all its vertexes, a counter of the number of the vertex in the graph, a counter of the number of edges and a counter of the number of changes that were made on the graph .
